WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
And here is Ronaldinho, picking up the ball near the halfway line.

00:05.000 --> 00:10.000
He's got past Ramos... effortlessly. He's into the box!

00:10.000 --> 00:15.000
A drop of the shoulder, past Helguera! It's a sensational run!

00:15.000 --> 00:18.000
[Crowd roaring loudly in the background]

00:18.000 --> 00:25.000
And the finish! It's magnificent! Absolutely magnificent from the Brazilian!

00:25.000 --> 00:30.000
Look at the stands. Look at the Real Madrid fans. They are standing up. They are applauding him!

00:30.000 --> 00:45.000
You rarely see this. The Santiago Bernabéu, rising to its feet to applaud a Barcelona player. That is the magic of Ronaldinho.

00:45.000 --> 00:55.000
[Prolonged applause and cheers]
